ional cost. Analyses using the single-column test case reveal that the\nwidth of the droplet size spectrum is affected by numerical diffusion pertinent\nto both spatial and spectral advection. Application of even a single corrective\niteration of MPDATA robustly decreases the relative dispersion of the droplet\nspectrum, roughly by a factor of two at the levels of maximal liquid water\ncontent.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 Nov 2020 12:07:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 2 Aug 2021 18:04:49 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 4 Aug 2021 13:07:50 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 13 Jan 2022 17:11:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-14"}
