y\nof whole-brain models for explaining the origin of large-scale cortical\noscillations and how they are shaped by the connectome.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 Nov 2020 12:18:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 3 Dec 2020 16:42:34 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 22 Mar 2021 09:13:58 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 1 Nov 2021 14:09:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-02"}
